						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  15
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC

						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  15
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  15
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  15
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

 SELECT id,title,alias ,category_id ,image , category_alias ,summary,created_time
						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,accessories,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 5

time:::0.00099992752075195

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  15
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 15

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  15
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

						  WHERE  record_id = 15 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id > 0  ORDER BY  id ASC

						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10

					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 3

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

 SELECT id,title,alias ,category_id ,image , category_alias ,summary,created_time
						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,accessories,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 5

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0.002000093460083

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10
						 

time:::0.002000093460083

					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 3 

time:::0.00099992752075195

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0.0010001659393311

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

time:::0.00099992752075195

			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

						  AND parent_id > 0  ORDER BY  id ASC

 SELECT id,title,alias ,category_id ,image , category_alias ,summary,created_time
						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6
						

time:::0.00099992752075195

						  WHERE published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 6

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,accessories,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 5

time:::0.0019998550415039

===========

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0.002000093460083

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10
						 

time:::0.003000020980835

===========

					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 3 

time:::0.010001182556152

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0.0039999485015869

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

time:::0.0019998550415039

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

					  FROM fs_order  WHERE sender_name <> "" AND sender_telephone <> "" ORDER BY  id DESC  LIMIT 10

SELECT name,created_time,id,email,comment,parent_id,level,record_id,is_admin,avatar  FROM fs_products_comments
						  WHERE  record_id = 3 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id = 0  ORDER BY  id DESC   LIMIT 0,3

===========

SELECT name,created_time,id,email,comment,parent_id,level,record_id,is_admin,avatar  FROM fs_products_comments
						  WHERE  record_id = 3 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id > 0  ORDER BY  id ASC  

time:::0.00099992752075195

						  WHERE  record_id = 3 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id = 0

						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1

						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

 SELECT id,title,alias ,category_id ,image , category_alias ,summary,created_time
						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6

						  WHERE published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 6

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,accessories,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 5

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10
						 

time:::0.0019998550415039

===========

 SELECT *
					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 3 

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

time:::0.00099992752075195

			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )

						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

 SELECT id,title,alias ,category_id ,image , category_alias ,summary,created_time
						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6
						

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id,title,summary,image, alias, category_id,category_alias
						  FROM fs_news
						  WHERE published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 6
						 

time:::0.0010008811950684

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,accessories,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 5

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT *
					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 3 

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

					  FROM fs_products_types  WHERE published = 1 ORDER BY ordering ASC

						WHERE product_id = 3

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT *
					  FROM fs_order  WHERE sender_name <> "" AND sender_telephone <> "" ORDER BY  id DESC  LIMIT 10

SELECT name,created_time,id,email,comment,parent_id,level,record_id,is_admin,avatar  FROM fs_products_comments
						  WHERE  record_id = 3 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id = 0  ORDER BY  id DESC   LIMIT 0,3 

time:::0

===========

SELECT name,created_time,id,email,comment,parent_id,level,record_id,is_admin,avatar  FROM fs_products_comments
						  WHERE  record_id = 3 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id > 0  ORDER BY  id ASC  

time:::0

===========

						  WHERE  record_id = 3 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id = 0

 SELECT id,title,alias ,category_id ,image , category_alias ,summary,created_time
						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,accessories,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 5

time:::0.0010001659393311

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10
						 

time:::0.002000093460083

					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 3 

time:::0.00099992752075195

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

time:::0.00099992752075195

			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

 SELECT id,title,alias ,category_id ,image , category_alias ,summary,created_time
						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,accessories,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 5

time:::0.00099992752075195

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 3 

time:::0.00099992752075195

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0.0010001659393311

			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id > 0  ORDER BY  id ASC

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10

						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

 SELECT id,title,alias ,category_id ,image , category_alias ,summary,created_time
						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6
						

time:::0.0010001659393311

						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 6

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,accessories,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 5

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0.0020008087158203

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10
						 

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT *
					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 3 

time:::0.00099992752075195

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0.002000093460083

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

time:::0.0010001659393311

			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

						  WHERE  record_id = 3 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id = 0  ORDER BY  id DESC   LIMIT 0,3 

time:::0

===========

SELECT name,created_time,id,email,comment,parent_id,level,record_id,is_admin,avatar  FROM fs_products_comments
						  WHERE  record_id = 3 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id > 0  ORDER BY  id ASC  

time:::0

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10

						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

				AND TABLE_SCHEMA = 'thosuadidong'

 SELECT id,title,alias ,category_id ,image , category_alias ,summary,created_time
						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6
						

time:::0.0019998550415039

===========

 SELECT id,title,summary,image, alias, category_id,category_alias
						  FROM fs_news
						  WHERE published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 6
						 

time:::0.0019998550415039

===========

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,accessories,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 5

time:::0.0030009746551514

===========

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0.003000020980835

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10
						 

time:::0.0019998550415039

===========

 SELECT *
					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 3 

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT *
					  FROM fs_order  WHERE sender_name <> "" AND sender_telephone <> "" ORDER BY  id DESC  LIMIT 10

SELECT name,created_time,id,email,comment,parent_id,level,record_id,is_admin,avatar  FROM fs_products_comments
						  WHERE  record_id = 3 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id = 0  ORDER BY  id DESC   LIMIT 0,3 

time:::0

===========

SELECT name,created_time,id,email,comment,parent_id,level,record_id,is_admin,avatar  FROM fs_products_comments
						  WHERE  record_id = 3 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id > 0  ORDER BY  id ASC  

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

SELECT count(*) FROM fs_products_comments
						  WHERE  record_id = 3 
								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id = 0

						  FROM fs_strengths
						 WHERE  published = 1 
						 ORDER BY  ordering ASC 
						 LIMIT 4

					FROM fs_menus_items
					WHERE published  = 1
						AND group_id = 1 
					ORDER BY ordering

					FROM fs_menus_items
					WHERE published  = 1
						AND group_id = 3 
					ORDER BY ordering

					WHERE published  = 1

 SELECT id,title,alias ,category_id ,image , category_alias ,summary,created_time
						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6
						

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT id,title,summary,image, alias, category_id,category_alias
						  FROM fs_news
						  WHERE published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 6
						 

time:::0.0079998970031738

===========

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,accessories,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 5

time:::0.002000093460083

===========

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0.0020010471343994

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT *
					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 3 

time:::0.00099992752075195

===========

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0

===========

					  FROM fs_products_types  WHERE published = 1 ORDER BY ordering ASC

						FROM fs_products_incentives AS a
						WHERE product_id = 3

						AND is_temporary = 1

===========

 SELECT *
					  FROM fs_products_filters
					  WHERE  tablename = "fs_products_tai_nghe" AND field_name = "manufactory" AND filter_value = "49" 

time:::0

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

time:::0

===========

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10

						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6

						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 5

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0.002000093460083

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10

					  FROM fs_products
					  WHERE id = 3

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5
						 

time:::0.00099992752075195

			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

								AND published = 1 
						  AND parent_id > 0  ORDER BY  id ASC

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

 SELECT id,title,alias ,category_id ,image , category_alias ,summary,created_time
						FROM fs_news 
						 WHERE published = 1 AND ( tags like '%AKG Q701%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe chính hãng%' OR  tags like '%tai nghe AKG%' )
						ORDER BY id DESC,ordering DESC
						LIMIT 0,6

 SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal  
						FROM fs_products
						WHERE category_id = 1 and manufactory = 49
							AND published = 1 ORDER BY ordering LIMIT 8

time:::0.002000093460083

===========

 SELECT  name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,category_id,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10

					  FROM fs_products

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  3
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

SELECT name,id , image,price,price_old,discount, alias,category_alias,quantity, price,price_old,types,manufactory_image,manufactory_name,date_start,date_end,warranty,is_hotdeal,summary,accessories
			 FROM fs_products WHERE published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_homepage = 1  AND is_new = 1
			ORDER BY  ordering DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

			 FROM fs_products  WHERE is_sell = 1 ORDER BY sale_count DESC, created_time DESC, id DESC LIMIT 0,5

						  WHERE ID IN ( 1,2,12,11,7,8,6,9,10,4 )
						  	AND id <>  15
						  	AND published = 1
						     ORDER BY  ordering DESC , id DESC
						     LIMIT 10

 SELECT id,name,summary,image,price,price_old,discount,types, alias,accessories, category_id,category_alias, ABS(price - 7990000) as price_subtract,manufactory_image,manufactory_name
						  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE published = 1
						  	AND id <>  15
						  	AND category_id =  1
						     ORDER BY price_subtract ASC
						     LIMIT 5

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%2%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

						 WHERE  published = 1 and category_published = 1 
						  ORDER BY   ordering DESC,created_time DESC
						 LIMIT 5

				WHERE module = "home" AND view = "home" AND ( task = "display" OR task = "" OR task IS NULL)

SELECT id,title,content, ordering, module, position, showTitle, params ,listItemid,news_categories,contents_categories,link_title
						FROM fs_blocks AS a 
						WHERE published = 1 
					ORDER BY ordering

					  WHERE published = 1 AND is_special = 1

 SELECT id,name, alias,tags_group,tablename,is_accessories, root_id, is_accessories,list_parents,icon,is_special
					FROM fs_products_categories 
					WHERE 
						show_in_homepage = 1 AND level = 0
					ORDER BY ordering
							

time:::0.0010001659393311

===========

 SELECT id,name,description,summary,image, created_time,category_id, category_alias, alias,price,price_old ,discount,published_double,image_double,date_end,date_start,warranty,types,is_hotdeal,accessories  FROM fs_products
						  WHERE 
						  	 published = 1  AND category_published = 1 AND show_in_home = 1
						  	 AND category_id_wrapper like '%1%'  ORDER BY  ordering DESC,created_time DESC, id DESC
						 LIMIT 10

time:::0.002000093460083

===========

 SELECT id,name, image, alias
							FROM fs_manufactories 
							WHERE published = 1  
							 AND tablenames like "%,fs_products_tai_nghe,%"
							 ORDER BY  ordering ASC,name ASC
